        {
            "title": "ASML第四季度訂單額創新高 AI投資浪潮洶湧提振需求",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Company filings, Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"555\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ynBGE33_MlWjQUtBPWI1iA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/09652f2f342f9c0feabeb76bda1d7f91\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Company filings, Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:ASML;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/ASML\">ASML</a>第四季度訂單額遠超分析師預期，得益於人工智能(AI)基礎設施快速發展提振對尖端晶片製造設備的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家荷蘭半導體設備製造商周三公佈，第四季度訂單額創出132億歐元（158億美元）的紀錄新高。彭博匯編的數據顯示，分析師的平均預期為68.5億歐元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASML是唯一一家生產製造先進半導體所需尖端光刻機的廠商，其客戶涵蓋台積電、英特爾等晶片製造領域的所有領軍企業。該公司的設備對生產輝達的AI加速器至關重要，這些加速器是數據中心訓練和運行AI模型的基石。這家荷蘭公司的訂單量是衡量晶片製造商對未來AI需求信心的一個晴雨表。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-14ce0614-3371-3826-a867-7c6c4294fc7a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TnifBMsNjjElW4PGvcrLmw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/34dd3e95c671d4e4d44304e0416fab61\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">AI熱潮在2026年延續，打破了市場對過度投資的擔憂，推動ASML市值本月突破5000億美元。 Meta Platforms Inc.和微軟等公司正斥資數千億美元建設數據中心，這促使晶片製造商擴大產能，進而推升了對ASML產品的需求。台積電本月表示，預計2026年資本支出將超過520億美元，其中大部分將投向先進製造技術。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管訂單強勁，ASML宣布計畫裁員約1,700人以實現組織精簡，受影響崗位主要在荷蘭，部分在美國。裁員數量相當於該公司員工總數的4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：ASML計畫在荷蘭和美國裁員約1,700人 主要涉及技術與IT部門</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">執行長Christophe Fouquet在接受彭博電視採訪時稱，「我們的表現很好，我們對此非常滿意，但即便是優秀的企業也需要改進」。他補充道，公司希望變得更加「敏捷」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASML股價在阿姆斯特丹市場一度上漲7.5%至1,309歐元，創下紀錄新高，年初至今漲幅擴大至41%。ASML的日本供應商，包括Lasertec Corp.、東京電子和Screen Holdings Co.，股價也都大幅走高。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"555\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sQ.EyuYVT0VB1Tl72II3Og--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/391f1a3eefd4d0255ffa0e9112b25cfe\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司2025年實現總淨銷售額327億歐元，預計今年營收在340億至390億歐元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國第四季度仍為ASML的最大市場，占淨系統銷售額的36%。財務長Roger Dassen在與記者的電話會議上表示，預計未來中國市場在營收方面的占比將降至約20%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"559\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AFDEiyjH8aTDTNiRuLT_NQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/35a6abed3dd5cffe07dba0e2224d7ddb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受美國主導的旨在遏制中國在半導體領域崛起的限制措施影響，ASML從未能向中國出售其EUV光刻機。該公司還被禁止向中國出售其最先進的DUV光刻設備。它向中國出口的設備要比最先進型號落後八代。儘管如此，中國晶片製造商仍在大量採購舊型號設備來生產成熟晶片。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASML未來在季度財報中將不再披露訂單數據，認為該指標無法準確反映業務發展勢頭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ASML’s Record Orders Beat Estimates as AI Spending Spurs Demand</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增第5-10段內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/asml%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E9%A1%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-ai%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE%E6%B4%B6%E6%B9%A7%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-063606030.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 19:28:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "軟銀據悉正在商談向OpenAI追加投資不超過300億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:軟銀;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/軟銀\">軟銀</a>集團正在商討向OpenAI追加投資不超過300億美元，顯示創始人孫正義希望在人工智能發展中扮演核心角色的雄心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀已是OpenAI的最大投資者之一。因討論未公開信息而要求匿名的知情人士稱，軟銀還在考慮向這家快速成長的人工智能公司追加投資。其中一位知情人士稱，軟銀正在考慮的最高投資額為300億美元，討論仍在進行中，投資規模可能會變化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受此消息提振，軟銀股價一度飆升8.8%，隨後收窄漲幅，周三東京午後交易時段上漲約 3.7%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7ef77390-eea1-30eb-acff-d594ad065599-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為提高軟銀在OpenAI的持股比例，並為一項旨在把人工智能注入所有設備的大規模投資備足資金，孫正義近期一直在調整資產配置。軟銀已出售所持輝達股份，並且最近暫停收購美國數據中心運營商Switch的談判。軟銀已累計持有OpenAI約11%的股份，並在上月剛投資了225億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀代表拒絕就這筆潛在投資置評。《華爾街日報》此前率先報導了這一消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SoftBank Is in Talks to Invest $30 Billion More in OpenAI (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alice French、Natasha Mascarenhas、Min-Jeong Lee、Jillian Ward、Vlad Savov.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%95%86%E8%AB%87%E5%90%91openai%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E300%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-042528393.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 12:59:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國以電力建設浪潮支持產業升級 四年新增裝機超過全美國電力容量",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"National Energy Administration; BloombergNEF\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"756\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tP0IfMCNoXd_yrYBN2URHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/08d53edb9c8243452772a8d480008c33\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">National Energy Administration; BloombergNEF</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國正在掀起一場全球罕見的能源擴建浪潮，全力保障關鍵高能耗設施的用電需求，而這些設施對於中國主宰未來的新興產業至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據國家能源局周三公佈的數據，去年中國新增各類發電裝機容量543吉瓦。這一規模比印度截至2024年底所有電廠的總裝機容量還要多出12%。中國自2021年底以來新增的發電裝機規模，也超過了整個美國電力系統的容量。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"756\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UlBhbwfOdKtqHr2gCRcD4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/aad0d0bec500aedac7694d3a9092369c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國國家主席習近平的目標，是確保能源供應穩定充裕，減少對進口燃料的依賴，並為人工智能、機器人製造和先進材料等快速成長且能源需求旺盛的產業提供競爭優勢。與此同時，外界日益擔心這些產業在美國的發展可能因缺乏廉價電力而受到掣肘。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a85e5653-3b7b-3ae8-b836-7deac917c0db-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「能源建設的推進力度依然非常強勁，各項數據都不斷刷新紀錄，」牛津能源研究所中國能源研究負責人Michal Meidan表示，「首要任務是保障能源供應安全，不僅如此，還要確保能源價格具有競爭力。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「能源必須服務於產業創新、工業升級和技術進步——這是中國‘十五五’規劃中經濟政策的核心，」Meidan說道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下，美國的電力需求似乎在數十年前已進入平台期，此後新增發電裝機速度明顯較慢。高盛集團全球大宗商品研究聯席主管Samantha Dart指出，隨著人工智能的快速發展，美國正竭力滿足數據中心等高耗能行業的用電需求，導致電力市場處於供應極為緊張的狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美國可能會面臨瓶頸，而中國似乎完全沒有遇到類似限制，」她說道，「美國目前在人工智能競賽中居於領導地位，但隨著時間推移，中國可能將逐步占據上風。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Four-Year Energy Spree Has Eclipsed Entire US Power Grid</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%A3%9D%E6%A9%9F%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F-080830669.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 17:09:46",
